No. 624. Charles Henry Davis, Trustee, Petitioner, v. George W. Bramblet. April 2, 1906. Mr. D. W. Lindsey, Mr. Frank Chinn and Mr. Richard W. Hale for petitioner.. Mr. Helm Bruce for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
